          <p class="text-lg text-secondary/70 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Calculate Short Term Accommodation (STA) costs for NDIS respite care. Get accurate pricing for weekdays, weekends, and public holidays using <strong>2025-26 NDIS rates</strong>.
          </p>

          <!-- Rate Card -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-6 border border-base-200 shadow-lg shadow-base-200/50 mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-secondary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
              <Icon name="hugeicons:bed-single-01" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
              NDIS STA Rates 2025-26
            </h3>
