              <p>NDIS respite care (Short Term Accommodation) costs vary by day type in 2025-26:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
                <li><strong>Weekday (Mon-Fri)</strong>: $346.51 per day</li>
                <li><strong>Saturday</strong>: $384.92 per day</li>
                <li><strong>Sunday</strong>: $423.32 per day</li>
                <li><strong>Public Holiday</strong>: $461.72 per day</li>
              </ul>
